                <h1>Orange Warning Signs: What They Mean</h1>
                <p>A sign with an orange background in a diamond or rectangular shape typically indicates caution. Such signs alert drivers and pedestrians to potential hazards or changes in conditions, like construction zones, hazardous intersections, or situations requiring increased awareness. Always heed caution signs for safety!</p>
